<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-bottom:12.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
<blockquote style=3D"margin-top:5.0pt;margin-bottom:5.0pt">
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">On 12 Sep 2025, at 5:37<span style=3D"font-family:&q=
uot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif">=E2=80=AF</span>PM,<span class=3D"apple-convert=
ed-space">&nbsp;</span><a href=3D"mailto:raffaellanz@icloud.com">raffaellan=
z@icloud.com</a><span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>wrote:<o=
:p></o:p></p>
